data.description: 'Motivated Sellers' Welcome to your newly renovated dream home! This beautiful house has been thoughtfully updated with modern finishes and fixtures, making it the perfect blend of style and comfort. The open-concept living area is perfect for entertaining guests, while the three cozy bedrooms provide a peaceful retreat at the end of a long day. The kitchen is bright and airy with stainless steel appliances. The home features a spacious back yard that is perfect for outdoor activities and relaxation. Located in a quiet and friendly neighborhood, this home is just minutes away from shopping, dining and entertainment. Don't miss out on this amazing opportunity to own your dream home!The home also features a sunroom that leads to a large back yard, perfect for outdoor activities and entertaining guests. The back yard is fully fenced, providing privacy.
